title: TOP OF THE ROCK
seo_title: Top of the Rock | WestHouse Hotel near Rockefeller Center
seo_description: Top of the Rock is a unique vantage point offering inspiring views from the top of Rockefeller Center. Dramatic panoramas of New York City unfold on all sides.
contents:
30 Rockefeller Plaza
212.698.2000

Hours vary by season Top of the Rock is a unique vantage point offering inspiring, unobstructed views from the top of Rockefeller Center. Dramatic panoramas of New York City unfold on all sides from this popular sightseeing destination.
